{"tid":1901870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸妺日本打尖搶口罩. 俾菲女及日漢打柒","createTime":"2020-02-28T05:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T06:06:10.000Z","uid":72009,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e2da7f61206bcca8f745782fb2228a48198442","tid":1901870,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"Share on system<br />\n<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\nA<br />\n疫船鑽石公主號早前停泊在日本橫濱港口，加上新冠肺炎疫情在日本燃燒，當地至今已錄得超過900宗確診個案，令到該國的口罩供不應求。有網民25日在Twitter上載影片，指中國女子在藥妝店插隊買口罩，遭菲律賓女子出言阻止，兩人由口角轉為大打出手，後來中國女的同行男子加入戰團，最終由一名見義勇為日本金髮男鎖喉，將內地女壓倒在地結束一場中日菲混戰的鬧劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200228/V7BJSPLJTEUZPGLNQ5NXBCTASU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200228%2FV7BJSPLJTEUZPGLNQ5NXBCTASU%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0ZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=d8794024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200228%2FV7BJSPLJTEUZPGLNQ5NXBCTASU%2F&h=33c0019f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200228/V7BJSPLJTEUZPGLNQ5NXBCTASU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好"},{"pid":"a1e339058260afaf761c945b6052abdfe89fcc06","tid":1901870,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"我宣佈，立法會我地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寸土必爭</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n功能組別最後一個月！決勝關鍵係工程、建築測量、飲食、批發零售、進出口！（附懶人包）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/atdRoLV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/atdRoLV</a>"},{"pid":"51bc9168437debf2a622493eebf9d9ad9ff09786","tid":1901870,"uid":73907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"鎖喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964a6cc9a64fd0e2014d82155a7880299480cff4","tid":1901870,"uid":298012,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"暴力係支那人唯一能理解㗎